import React from 'react'
import { Button } from 'react-scroll'
import Video from '../../Videos/TeamVB.mp4'
import{
    TemaContainer,
    VdoBG,
    TeamBG,
    TeamContent,
    TeamH1,
    TeamP,
    ButtonWrper,
    ArrowForward,
    ArrowRight
} from './TeamElements'


const Team = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <TemaContainer>
                <TeamBG>
                    <VdoBG autoPlay loop muted src={Video} type='video/mp4'/>
                </TeamBG>
                <TeamContent>
                    <TeamH1>Team Visible</TeamH1>
                    <TeamP>
                        AutoPlay slider
                    </TeamP>
                </TeamContent>
                <ButtonWrper>
                    <Button to="signup">
                        Sign UP {hover ? <ArrowForward/> : <ArrowRight/>}
                    </Button>
                </ButtonWrper>
            </TemaContainer>  
        </>
    )
}

export default Team
